Calculate Triage Effectiveness with Bootstrap

Source: R/calc_te.R
calculate_te_bootstrap.Rd

Calculate Triage Effectiveness with Bootstrap

calculate_te_bootstrap(
  df,
  bootstrap_params,
  n_workers,
  subgroup,
  var1,
  var2,
  min_loset_warning,
  seed
)

Arguments

df

Data frame containing patient data

bootstrap_params

List of bootstrap parameters

n_workers

Number of workers for parallel processing

subgroup

Optional list for subgroup analysis

var1

Optional string for first comparison variable

var2

Optional string for second comparison variable

min_loset_warning

will be sent onward to check if a valid amount of loset cases exists

Value

List containing metrics, distributions, and convergence information

Details

Performs bootstrap analysis of TE metrics with parallel processing and progress tracking.
